title: Evans, Palatka storm past Menendez in key district clash
text:
Evans, Palatka storm past Menendez in key district clash 
Sat, Oct 17, 2015 @ 12:11 am 
PALATKA 30 
MENENDEZ 0 
Dontaeveone Evans rushed for three second-half scores, pulling the Panthers clear of visiting Menendez (3-4, 1-2 District 5-5A)... James Campbell opened the scoring for Palatka (3-4, 2-1) with a 24-yard touchdown pass to Markell Rasher... Palatkaâ€™s Eron Carter and Robert Passmore forced turnovers as the Panthers held Menendez to 191 total yards.
